    file: {
      fileName: "uploaded_file.pdf",
      content: fileBuffer,
    },
    purpose: "ocr"
  });
```

The `purpose` type `ocr` is not inside the `FilePurpose` type: 

![Image](https://github.com/user-attachments/assets/c31e3ab8-d01c-47ca-abc7-38ce2447eaf4)

Current `FilePurpose` type definition: https://github.com/mistralai/client-ts/blob/a3fd01f80c13afdce089e61705260f21382579ed/src/models/components/filepurpose.ts#L12C1-L16C56

```
export const FilePurpose = {
